      and to keep your direction under pressure.
    </p>

    <h2>Gaman in practice</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>maintain movement quality even when tired,</li>
      <li>do not chase shortcuts at the expense of fundamentals,</li>
      <li>treat difficult periods as part of maturation.</li>
    </ul>

